charges.charge_description: 21:952(a), 960(a)(1) and 960(b)(2)(B)(ii); 18:3551 et seq. NARCOTICS-IMPORTATION/EXPORTATION-did knowingly and intentionally import cocaine, a Sch. II narcotic drug controlled substance. (1)

charges.charge_disposition: Defendant is hereby committed to the custody of the U.S. Bureau of Prisons to be imprisoned for a term of 30 months. Upon release from Imprisonment, defendant shall be on supervised release for a term of 36 months WITH THE CONDITION THAT THE DEFENDANT RECEIVE PSYCHOLOGICAL COUNSELING. (1)

charges.charge_description: 21:841(a)(1) and 841(b)(1)(B)(ii)(II); 18:3551 et seq. NARCOTICS-SELL, DISTRIBUTE, OR DISPENSE-did possess with intent to distribute cocaine, a Sch. II narcotic drug controlled substance. (2)

charges.charge_disposition: Open Counts are dismissed on the motion of the United States. (2)
